        The  duties  and  responsibilities  of  the


        Academic Council shall be as follows:




                a) Determine,  review  and  recommend


        for  approval  of  the  Board  of  Regents,  the

        academic programs including academic rules

        and regulations of the University;





                b) Devise/draft,  review  and  recommend

